{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2011/07/big-rain/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/knowledge/","name":"见闻杂事"}],"tags":[{"name":"天气","path":"/tag/weather/"},{"name":"宜昌","path":"/tag/yichang/"},{"name":"朋友","path":"/tag/friends/"},{"name":"电影","path":"/tag/movie/"}],"featured_media":null,"path":"/2011/07/big-rain/","date":"2011-07-31T03:27:00.000Z","excerpt":"7月30日买好了票，和朋友们去万达看《变形金刚3》，下午3点天气突变狂风暴雨，我顶把伞出门5分钟就已经全湿了， … ","title":"7月30日在宜昌看海","content":"<p>7月30日买好了票，和朋友们去万达看《变形金刚3》，下午3点天气突变狂风暴雨，我顶把伞出门5分钟就已经全湿了，雷声不断，走在路上所有车的报警都在叫，四周空无一人，感觉像末日。下西坝江边的鱼馆子被掀了3、4个，路上的积水没过人行道的台阶，罕见啊。</p>\n<p><object width=\"550\" height=\"400\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"pluginspage\" value=\"http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer\" /><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XMjkwNjQ0MTY4/v.swf\" /><param name=\"play\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"loop\" value=\"loop\" /><param name=\"menu\" value=\"true\" /><embed width=\"550\" height=\"400\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XMjkwNjQ0MTY4/v.swf\" pluginspage=\"http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer\" play=\"true\" loop=\"loop\" menu=\"true\" /></object></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2011/07/big-rain/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3675143411","4019104361"]}